(18, 'Generic Diflucan', '150mg / 200mg', 'Fluconazole', '1.37', '/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Anti%20Fungal/fluconazol.png', 6, 'Generic Diflucan (Fluconazole) - Anti Fungal Treatment Pills', '<p>Fungal as well as yeast infections are not very common but can be very fatal. Hence on has to be very careful if he or she has any kind of yeast or fungal infection. You have number of medications offered to you for the treatment of such infections. Some medications work wonders whereas some do not prove to be working at all. You have to be very selective when it comes to getting the medication for such infections because if you select the wrong medication, the conditions might worsen.&nbsp;<strong>One medication you can blindly rely on is fluconazole.</strong>&nbsp;This medication is basically used for the prevention as well as treatment of a huge variety of yeast and fungal infections. This medicine primarily belongs to a particular class of medications known as azole antifungals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How does it work?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It acts by impeding the growth of some particular types of fungus. This medication is also well known by the name of Diflucan. You can use Diflucan for thrush as well. Diflucan is another name of this medication.&nbsp;<em>You can get fluconazole conveniently over the web and offline as well.</em>&nbsp;Most of the people prefer buying it online as it is cheaper online and it also saves a lot of time. You can make the payment after the delivery of the product. You can rest assure that the product will reach your place as soon as you place your order. As far as the prescription is concerned, you can submit a scanned copy of the prescription to the websites. In case you are not able to find fluconazole tablet, you can look for Diflucan or Diflucan for thrush.</p>\r\n', '<p>Consumption of one oral fluconazole tablet of 150 mg to around ten lactating women surprising resulted in the mean Cmax of 2.60 mL ranging from 1.57 to 3.65 mL. stable state concentrati